<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<opml version="1.0">
  <head>
    <title>Life goals</title>
    <expansionState>1,5,8,11</expansionState>
  </head>
  <body>
    <outline text="AKA &quot;things that I want to be true when I am fifty&quot;"/>
    <outline text="Primary Goals">
      <outline text="I want to be a valuable and intimate friend with a lot of people. I want to leave behind a trail of whole relationships. This extends to family. "/>
      <outline text="I want to know Scripture"/>
      <outline text="I want to be a part of bringing the Gospel to every tribe, tongue and nation around the globe, in a personal, relational way (with at least part of that)"/>
      <outline text="I want to be active in ministry in the United States. All my friends and family are here, and I don't want to consign this nation to hell or abandon my relationships">
        <outline text="I don't think that I'll spend my whole life overseas. If I do, this will have to change."/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="I want to be involved enough in politics to know what's going on, be able to discuss it intelligently, and act when I can do so"/>
      <outline text="I want to not lose touch with the new generation, especially the generation of my children. I need to be able to relate to them and talk to them about issues.">
        <outline text="I want to remember the dynamics of the child-adult relationships I had, and never replicate the things that gave me such intense frustration as I had at times / a lot. "/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="I want to have a healthy view of relationships, women, children, the elderly, authority, things that annoy me in other people, needy people, proud people, homosexuals, &quot;sinners&quot;, the lost, and everything else that I do not fully understnad, falsely judge, or sin against with unholy prejudice. "/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="Secondary Goals">
      <outline text="I want to make enough money to be comfortable"/>
      <outline text="I want to still know my way around computers"/>
      <outline text="I want to know and understand the philosophy, art, music, and so forth of the age, and be able to discuss it intelligently. "/>
    </outline>
  </body>
</opml>
